(24, 'Clement Loder', 'Contact Us Form', '2024-03-20 01:54:44', '<div class=\"form_table\" style=\"width:700px; height:auto; font-size:12px; color:#333333; letter-spacing:1px; line-height:20px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n			<div style=\"border:8px double #c3c3d0; padding:12px;\">\n			<div align=\"center\" style=\"color:#990000; font-style:italic; font-size:20px; font-family:Arial; margin:bottom: 15px;\">(Contact Us Form)</div>\n\n			<table width=\"90%\" cellspacing=\"2\" cellpadding=\"5\" align=\"center\" style=\"font-family:Verdana; font-size:13px\">\n				<tr><td><b>First Name</b>:</td> <td>Clement</td></tr><tr><td><b>Last Name</b>:</td> <td>Loder</td></tr><tr><td><b>Address</b>:</td> <td>Borgartuni 73</td></tr><tr><td><b>Email Address</b>:</td> <td>loder.clement@outlook.com</td></tr><tr><td><b>Phone</b>:</td> <td>4489426</td></tr><tr><td><b>Question or Comment</b>:</td> <td>Dear Sir,\r\n\r\nGoogle&#039;s &quot;Helpful Content Update&quot; got you down again?\r\n\r\nAt SEO-Depot.com we offer a range of SEO services that will recover and maintain rankings.\r\n\r\nOur Link-Building Strategies grow and expand your rankings and range of keywords dramactically with 100% succes rate.\r\n\r\nWe offer Link-Building Services and SEO training and advice tailored to your website&#039;s SEO needs.\r\nor Full SEO onsite Services.\r\n\r\nLocal SEO is available for local businesses that will change the way you think about Local SEO.\r\nMore Terms, brnad matching services, and locations by city, county or province.\r\n\r\nShopping Site? No worries, we&#039;ll show you how to maximize your exposure!\r\n\r\nWith Chat GPT being used to create ranking content and Google&#039;s Generative AI Experience, competing is more challenging than ever.\r\n\r\nOur training or Full EO services for content creation for blogs will help you gain the ranking authority your site needs.\r\n\r\nMost Important is our services are affordable!\r\n\r\n\r\nSEO Depot\r\nhttps://seo-depot.com/offer/\r\n\r\nWe also offer FREE website audits for a technical analysis of your site and customized SEO best coaching practices for your site, and more so you can maximize SEO results.\r\n\r\nOur services work for the local SEO business to Global SEO Requirements, inflating websites precedence and responses to searches more broadly\r\nand with greater performance.\r\n\r\nExperience a new approach to SEO! Reach out to us wuth our on-sit chat app.\r\n\r\nLet us show you what we can do for your business&#039;s website promotion. Request a Free SEO Audit!\r\n\r\nHope you find this useful,\r\n\r\nSales@seo-depot.com</td></tr>\n			</table>\n\n			</div>\n			</div>', 'new', 'inbox', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
