(5, 1, '2020-07-06 06:46:35', '2020-07-06 06:46:35', 'A village empowerment charity organization in Massachusetts focused halfway across the world to a small village in central Kenya called Karia. We are an organization dedicated to uplift the status of an impoverished rural plantation village by the essential means of education by which we intend to make permanent changes for the better. \r\n\r\nOur singular goal is to improve learning in Karia by uplifting the substandard educational conditions. Weâll do this by upgrading its dilapidated classrooms, building a library and a computer lab, providing proper student desks, bringing up-to-date school materials, constructing a sports field, establishing a community library, and more.\r\n', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2020-07-08 03:59:10', '2020-07-08 03:59:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/home', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(6, 1, '2020-07-06 06:46:35', '2020-07-06 06:46:35', '', 'Sitemap', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sitemap', '', '', '2020-07-06 06:46:35', '2020-07-06 06:46:35', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/sitemap', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(7, 1, '2020-07-06 06:51:43', '2020-07-06 06:51:43', 'In our modern world, the results of inadequate education run very deep. People who lack the necessary skills and mindsets find it difficult to keep up with the change. Postponing education longer shrinks the chances of success to zero. We are not here to preach the danger but to display a ray of hope. \r\n\r\nOur plans center on elevating the village of Karia from substandard conditions into a student-friendly learning environment. For this, we currently have two ongoing projects in Karia. If we succeed here, we will leave an instructive mark on the village, its neighbors, and finally to Kenya as a whole. As we move on to other villages, we can proudly tell the world that we have proven the significance of our kind of endeavor.  \r\n\r\n<div class=\"serv_list\">\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/karia-primary-school.jpg\" alt=\"a teacher in karia teaching the students\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-primary-school\"><span>First Project - Karia Primary School</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/nonhome-88540994.jpg\"  alt=\"a man smiling in the library\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-community-library\"><span>Second Project - Karia Community Library</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Programs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-programs', '', '', '2020-07-08 10:46:24', '2020-07-08 10:46:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2020-07-06 06:51:51', '2020-07-06 06:51:51', 'Join us and take part in the developments on the ground. The most appreciable form of help we can get is your time and skills to actualize our endeavor. Be part of us through the form below!\r\n\r\n[form src=\"volunteerForm\"]', 'Volunteer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-volunteer', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:27:04', '2020-07-08 05:27:04', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2020-07-06 06:52:02', '2020-07-06 06:52:02', 'Here are the sponsors behind this project. We are grateful for their kindness. Our success is born out of their charity.\r\n\r\nTo be a sponsor, you can have us notified right away. Use this electronic form.\r\n\r\n[pof src=\"sponsorship\"]\r\n', 'Sponsorship', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-sponsorship', '', '', '2024-01-18 05:51:49', '2024-01-18 05:51:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2020-07-06 06:48:54', '2020-07-06 06:48:54', '<div class=\"nh_mv\" id=\"mission\">\r\n<figure> <img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/thumb-1298862454.jpg\" alt=\"lady volunteer giving the donation to the old lady\"> </figure>\r\n<h2>Mission and Vision</h2>\r\n<p>To improve learning in Karia primary school through upgrading dilapidated classrooms, building a library and computer lab, providing proper students desks and up-to-date learning materials, and improving sport fields. Also, we plan to build a community library to benefit village members who are not in school.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"nh_dummy\">\r\n<p>Fountain of Wisdom is a non-profit charity organization registered in the state of Massachusetts whose purpose is to eliminate poverty in the small village of Karia in central Kenya through better, modern education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karia is a poor village located in the central part of Kenya. There are no industries or manufacturing companies in this part of the world. Most residents work as casual laborers at nearby coffee plantations, while others perform manual jobs in the community. Those fortunate to own a piece of land are subsistence farmers, rearing cows, or growing vegetables, and earning a living by selling their produce.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Although the government is promoting education, it contributes a very small amount towards the funding of schools. Karia has only one primary school but it is in poor condition. The existing classrooms are dilapidated and overcrowded. Studentsâ desks are falling apart and teachers are using archaic materials to teach. Student toilets are in an unhygienic state. The school has no library, no computer lab, nor a student knowledge center. The playing field has been neglected for a long time and is overgrown with vegetation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As of result of substandard education, more than half of Kariaâs residents lack formal employment because they lack the skills needed in todayâs job market. If changes in how students are educated are not done soon, their chance of succeeding out of poverty is almost zero.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To learn more about Karia and what we do, see our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-gallery\']\">photo gallery</a> and our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-programs\']\">programs</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTalk to us today! <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-about-us', '', '', '2020-08-14 16:30:01', '2020-08-14 16:30:01', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2020-07-06 06:50:52', '2020-07-06 06:50:52', 'You are more than qualified to contribute to improving Karia and the Kenyan people. Donate through the form below. \r\n\r\n[pof src=\"donation\"]\r\n\r\n', 'Donate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-donate', '', '', '2024-01-18 05:36:54', '2024-01-18 05:36:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
