(37, 1, '2020-07-06 06:57:31', '2020-07-06 06:57:31', 'You are reading dummy text as placeholders for this layout. Contents are for display purposes only. Dummy text for the reader to review. Words shown on this layout are placeholders.\r\n\r\nThese contents are temporary and are for display purposes only.  We can post company information here. Such space is reserved for the reader to learn more about the business, its products and services.  Words shown on this layout are placeholders. This space is reserved for more details about the company.\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-06 06:57:31', '2020-07-06 06:57:31', '', 5, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/5-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
