(40, 1, '2020-07-06 07:16:01', '2020-07-06 07:16:01', 'The mission to improve quality education standards in a backwater village is not easy. We will need all the help we can get. If you would like to lend us a hand, here are the ways you can assist. We will make sure that the people of Karia know the people behind the ambition of a better future for them.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"nh_btn\">\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">Donate</a>\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-volunteer\']\">Volunteer</a>\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-sponsorship\']\">Sponsor Us</a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Support Our Advocacy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nonprofit-organization-support-our-advocacy', '', '', '2020-07-08 12:09:13', '2020-07-08 12:09:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/abuga/fountainlu/?page_id=40', 0, 'page', '', 0),
