(62, 1, '2020-07-08 03:59:10', '2020-07-08 03:59:10', 'A village empowerment charity organization in Massachusetts focused halfway across the world to a small village in central Kenya called Karia. We are an organization dedicated to uplift the status of an impoverished rural plantation village by the essential means of education by which we intend to make permanent changes for the better. \r\n\r\nOur singular goal is to improve learning in Karia by uplifting the substandard educational conditions. Weâll do this by upgrading its dilapidated classrooms, building a library and a computer lab, providing proper student desks, bringing up-to-date school materials, constructing a sports field, establishing a community library, and more.\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 03:59:10', '2020-07-08 03:59:10', '', 5, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/5-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(63, 1, '2020-07-08 05:08:19', '2020-07-08 05:08:19', '<div class=\"nh_dummy\">\r\nFountain of Wisdom is a non-profit charity organization registered in the state of Massachusetts whose purpose is to eliminate poverty in the small village of Karia in central Kenya through better, modern education.\r\n\r\nKaria is a poor village located in the central part of Kenya. There are no industries or manufacturing companies in this part of the world. Most residents work as casual laborers at nearby coffee plantations, while others perform manual jobs in the community. Those fortunate to own a piece of land are subsistence farmers, rearing cows, or growing vegetables, and earning a living by selling their produce.\r\n\r\nAlthough the government is promoting education, it contributes a very small amount towards the funding of schools. Karia has only one primary school but it is in poor condition. The existing classrooms are dilapidated and overcrowded. Studentsâ desks are falling apart and teachers are using archaic materials to teach. Student toilets are in an unhygienic state. The school has no library, no computer lab, nor a student knowledge center. The playing field has been neglected for a long time and is overgrown with vegetation.\r\n\r\nAs of result of substandard education, more than half of Kariaâs residents lack formal employment because they lack the skills needed in todayâs job market. If changes in how students are educated are not done soon, their chance of succeeding out of poverty is almost zero.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about Karia and what we do, see our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-gallery\']\">photo gallery</a> and our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-programs\']\">programs</a>.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"nh_mv\" id=\"mission\">\r\n<p>To improve learning in Karia primary school through upgrading dilapidated classrooms, building a library and computer lab, providing proper students desks and up-to-date learning materials, and improving sport fields. Also, we plan to build a community library to benefit village members who are not in school.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTalk to us today! <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:08:19', '2020-07-08 05:08:19', '', 10, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/10-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(64, 1, '2020-07-08 05:09:11', '2020-07-08 05:09:11', '<div class=\"nh_dummy\">\r\nFountain of Wisdom is a non-profit charity organization registered in the state of Massachusetts whose purpose is to eliminate poverty in the small village of Karia in central Kenya through better, modern education.\r\n\r\nKaria is a poor village located in the central part of Kenya. There are no industries or manufacturing companies in this part of the world. Most residents work as casual laborers at nearby coffee plantations, while others perform manual jobs in the community. Those fortunate to own a piece of land are subsistence farmers, rearing cows, or growing vegetables, and earning a living by selling their produce.\r\n\r\nAlthough the government is promoting education, it contributes a very small amount towards the funding of schools. Karia has only one primary school but it is in poor condition. The existing classrooms are dilapidated and overcrowded. Studentsâ desks are falling apart and teachers are using archaic materials to teach. Student toilets are in an unhygienic state. The school has no library, no computer lab, nor a student knowledge center. The playing field has been neglected for a long time and is overgrown with vegetation.\r\n\r\nAs of result of substandard education, more than half of Kariaâs residents lack formal employment because they lack the skills needed in todayâs job market. If changes in how students are educated are not done soon, their chance of succeeding out of poverty is almost zero.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about Karia and what we do, see our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-gallery\']\">photo gallery</a> and our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-programs\']\">programs</a>.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"nh_mv\" id=\"mission\">\r\n<h2>Mission and Vision</h2>\r\n<p>To improve learning in Karia primary school through upgrading dilapidated classrooms, building a library and computer lab, providing proper students desks and up-to-date learning materials, and improving sport fields. Also, we plan to build a community library to benefit village members who are not in school.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTalk to us today! <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:09:11', '2020-07-08 05:09:11', '', 10, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/10-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(65, 1, '2020-07-08 05:17:12', '2020-07-08 05:17:12', 'You are more than qualified to contribute to improving Karia and the Kenyan people. Donate through the form below. \r\n\r\n[form src=\"paypal_donation\"]', 'Donate', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:17:12', '2020-07-08 05:17:12', '', 11, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/11-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(66, 1, '2020-07-08 05:23:46', '2020-07-08 05:23:46', 'A library is not only about lending books. It is a creative space where skills and talents are nurtured. A community library will provide a variety of reading materials, both physical and electronic format. It will help nurture the culture of reading and learning in the community.\r\n\r\nThe library will provide free internet which is currently unaffordable to the residents. The Internet bypasses physical barriers to communication and allows humans to interact easily on a global scale. Through search engines, worldwide information will be brought closer to Karia residents.\r\n\r\nOlder people will have a place to meet and network. This will make an enormous difference to those individuals with amazing ideas but do not know where to start. By utilizing resources provided in the library, they will learn and be empowered to solve some of the prevailing social challenges such as corruption, hunger, preventable diseases (malaria, cholera, HIV), and environment denigration.\r\n\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Karia Community Library', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'karia-community-library', '', '', '2020-07-08 06:44:19', '2020-07-08 06:44:19', '', 7, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/?page_id=66', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(67, 1, '2020-07-08 05:23:55', '2020-07-08 05:23:55', 'We first have to improve the education standards in Karia primary school by setting up modern infrastructures that will enable 21st-century education.\r\n\r\nThis follows five steps.\r\n\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Upgrade classrooms to be student-centered and a conducive learning environment. Also, provide classrooms that cater to students with disabilities.\r\n<li>Build a school library with modern reading materials, and equipped with technology for students to collaborate with students in developed countries.\r\n<li>Build a computer lab to introduce computer learning at an early stage. A few decades ago basic reading was the way out of poverty, but into today\'s world, basic computer skills are necessities to succeed in life.\r\n<li>Construct new toilets. The current students\' toilets are in deplorable and unhygienic conditions which pose a great risk of spreading communicable diseases to the most vulnerable in the society.\r\n<li>Improve the playing field so that students can participate in sporting activities. Presently, the playing field is overgrown with vegetation making it unusable.\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Karia Primary School', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'karia-primary-school', '', '', '2020-07-08 06:05:05', '2020-07-08 06:05:05', '', 7, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/?page_id=67', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(68, 1, '2020-07-08 05:23:46', '2020-07-08 05:23:46', '', 'Karia Community Library', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '66-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:23:46', '2020-07-08 05:23:46', '', 66, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/66-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(69, 1, '2020-07-08 05:23:55', '2020-07-08 05:23:55', '', 'Karia Primary School', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '67-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:23:55', '2020-07-08 05:23:55', '', 67, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/67-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2020-07-08 05:24:24', '2020-07-08 05:24:24', 'In our modern world, the results of inadequate education run very deep. People who lack the necessary skills and mindsets find it difficult to keep up with the change. Postponing education longer shrinks the chances of success to zero. We are not here to preach the danger but to display a ray of hope. \r\n\r\nOur plans center on elevating the village of Karia from substandard conditions into a student-friendly learning environment. For this, we currently have two ongoing projects in Karia. If we succeed here, we will leave an instructive mark on the village, its neighbors, and finally to Kenya as a whole. As we move on to other villages, we can proudly tell the world that we have proven the significance of our kind of endeavor.  \r\n\r\n<div class=\"serv_list\">\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/xxxx.jpg\" alt=\"karia-primary-school\"><figcaption><a href=\"xxx\"><span>First Project - Karia Primary School</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/xxxx.jpg\"  alt=\"karia-community-library\"><figcaption><a href=\"xxxx\"><span>Second Project - Karia Community Library</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Programs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:24:24', '2020-07-08 05:24:24', '', 7, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/7-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(71, 1, '2020-07-08 05:27:04', '2020-07-08 05:27:04', 'Join us and take part in the developments on the ground. The most appreciable form of help we can get is your time and skills to actualize our endeavor. Be part of us through the form below!\r\n\r\n[form src=\"volunteerForm\"]', 'Volunteer', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:27:04', '2020-07-08 05:27:04', '', 8, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/8-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(72, 1, '2020-07-08 05:28:05', '2020-07-08 05:28:05', 'Here are the sponsors behind this project. We are grateful for their kindness. Our success is born out of their charity.\r\n<div class=\"comingsoon mb30\">List of sponsors here...</div>\r\n\r\nTo be a sponsor, you can have us notified right away. Use this electronic form.\r\n\r\n\r\n[form src=\"paypal_sponsorship\"]', 'Sponsorship', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:28:05', '2020-07-08 05:28:05', '', 9, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/9-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
