(74, 1, '2020-07-08 05:31:36', '2020-07-08 05:31:36', 'If you want to talk to us, our contact number is 978-918-6391. You may reach us through the email lucmuiruri@gmail.com for our news feed and progress report, or talk to us through this message board. \r\n\r\n[form src=\"contactForm\"]', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:31:36', '2020-07-08 05:31:36', '', 19, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/19-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(75, 1, '2020-07-08 05:35:18', '2020-07-08 05:35:18', 'The mission to improve quality education standards in a backwater village is not easy. We will need all the help we can get. If you would like to lend us a hand, here are the ways you can assist. We will make sure that the people of Karia know the people behind the ambition of a better future for them.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"nh_btn\">\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">Donate</a>\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-volunteer\']\">Volunteer</a>\r\n  <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-sponsorship\']\">Sponsor Us</a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Support Our Advocacy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '40-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:35:18', '2020-07-08 05:35:18', '', 40, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/40-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(76, 1, '2020-07-08 05:38:40', '2020-07-08 05:38:40', 'In our modern world, the results of inadequate education run very deep. People who lack the necessary skills and mindsets find it difficult to keep up with the change. Postponing education longer shrinks the chances of success to zero. We are not here to preach the danger but to display a ray of hope. \r\n\r\nOur plans center on elevating the village of Karia from substandard conditions into a student-friendly learning environment. For this, we currently have two ongoing projects in Karia. If we succeed here, we will leave an instructive mark on the village, its neighbors, and finally to Kenya as a whole. As we move on to other villages, we can proudly tell the world that we have proven the significance of our kind of endeavor.  \r\n\r\n<div class=\"serv_list\">\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/xxxx.jpg\" alt=\"xxx\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-primary-school\"><span>First Project - Karia Primary School</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/xxxx.jpg\"  alt=\"xxx\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-community-library\"><span>Second Project - Karia Community Library</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Programs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:38:40', '2020-07-08 05:38:40', '', 7, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/7-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(77, 1, '2020-07-08 05:40:50', '2020-07-08 05:40:50', 'We first have to improve the education standards in Karia primary school by setting up modern infrastructures that will enable 21st-century education.\r\n\r\nThis follows five steps.\r\n\r\n<ol type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Upgrade classrooms to be student-centered and a conducive learning environment. Also, provide classrooms that cater to students with disabilities.\r\n<li>Build a school library with modern reading materials, and equipped with technology for students to collaborate with students in developed countries.\r\n<li>Build a computer lab to introduce computer learning at an early stage. A few decades ago basic reading was the way out of poverty, but into today\'s world, basic computer skills are necessities to succeed in life.\r\n<li>Construct new toilets. The current students\' toilets are in deplorable and unhygienic conditions which pose a great risk of spreading communicable diseases to the most vulnerable in the society.\r\n<li>Improve the playing field so that students can participate in sporting activities. Presently, the playing field is overgrown with vegetation making it unusable.\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Karia Primary School', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '67-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 05:40:50', '2020-07-08 05:40:50', '', 67, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/67-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
