(116, 1, '2020-07-08 06:41:03', '2020-07-08 06:41:03', 'A library is not only about lending books. It is a creative space where skills and talents are nurtured. A community library will provide a variety of reading materials, both physical and electronic format. It will help nurture the culture of reading and learning in the community.\n\nThe library will provide free internet which is currently unaffordable to the residents. The Internet bypasses physical barriers to communication and allows humans to interact easily on a global scale. Through search engines, worldwide information will be brought closer to Karia residents.\n\nOlder people will have a place to meet and network. This will make an enormous difference to those individuals with amazing ideas but do not know where to start. By utilizing resources provided in the library, they will learn and be empowered to solve some of the prevailing social challenges such as corruption, hunger, preventable diseases (malaria, cholera, HIV), and environment denigration.\n\n\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\n', 'Karia Community Library', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '66-autosave-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 06:41:03', '2020-07-08 06:41:03', '', 66, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/66-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(118, 1, '2020-07-08 06:42:58', '2020-07-08 06:42:58', 'In our modern world, the results of inadequate education run very deep. People who lack the necessary skills and mindsets find it difficult to keep up with the change. Postponing education longer shrinks the chances of success to zero. We are not here to preach the danger but to display a ray of hope. \r\n\r\nOur plans center on elevating the village of Karia from substandard conditions into a student-friendly learning environment. For this, we currently have two ongoing projects in Karia. If we succeed here, we will leave an instructive mark on the village, its neighbors, and finally to Kenya as a whole. As we move on to other villages, we can proudly tell the world that we have proven the significance of our kind of endeavor.  \r\n\r\n<div class=\"serv_list\">\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/karia-primary-school.jpg\" alt=\"a teacher in karia teaching the students\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-primary-school\"><span>First Project - Karia Primary School</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/nonhome-88540994.jpg\"  alt=\"a man smiling in the library\"><figcaption><a href=\"karia-community-library\"><span>Second Project - Karia Community Library</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTake part in the movement. <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'Programs', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '7-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 06:42:58', '2020-07-08 06:42:58', '', 7, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/7-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
