(124, 1, '2020-07-08 10:52:38', '2020-07-08 10:52:38', 'If you want to talk to us, our contact number is 978-918-6391. You may reach us through the email <a href=\"mailto:lucmuiruri@gmail.com\">lucmuiruri@gmail.com</a> for our news feed and progress report, or talk to us through this message board. \r\n\r\n[form src=\"contactForm\"]', 'Contact Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '19-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-08 10:52:38', '2020-07-08 10:52:38', '', 19, 'https://web6.proweaverlinks.com/fountainlu/19-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
