udent knowledge center. The playing field has been neglected for a long time and is overgrown with vegetation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As of result of substandard education, more than half of Kariaâs residents lack formal employment because they lack the skills needed in todayâs job market. If changes in how students are educated are not done soon, their chance of succeeding out of poverty is almost zero.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To learn more about Karia and what we do, see our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-gallery\']\">photo gallery</a> and our <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-programs\']\">programs</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nTalk to us today! <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-contact-us\']\">Send us a message</a> and <a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'nonprofit-organization-donate\']\">donate</a>.\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-14 16:26:09', '2020-08-14 16:26:09', '', 10, 'http://www.fountainwisdom.org/10-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
